/* ===============================================================
   SAFETYPRO — PHASE 2: GLOBAL COLOR REMAP (flower garden → professional)
   Target bright saturated colors used in inline styles and convert to muted tokens.
   =============================================================== */

/* ==== 1. KILL BRIGHT GREEN #22C55E (Tailwind green-500) — replace with muted #10B981 ==== */
